name: Mary W.
text: First tip - Order ahead. Our pizza was super today! Thin crust, brushed with garlic butter. The small salads are huge! No need to order a large! I've gone in person to order, & they are generally slow. But, a very good choice for carry out!

Diane is an asset to their company every year she makes us feel so special after 8 years of going there we feel like family and would never go anywhere else on July 6th. Food is amazing I know that's kinda crazy to say about a pizza chain, however it is a must try.
